    • createStemmedKey

      public java.lang.String createStemmedKey​(gov.va.chir.model.LexicalElement pTerm)
      createStemmedKey includes a key that is the uninflected, lowercased, term or if not from the dictionary, normalized by these rules if all numbers, the numbers if all punctuation, null if a combination of punctuation and numbers the same form if a contains letters then it gets porter stemmed, lowercased and trimmed. This tool uses the openNLP version of the porter stemmer
      Parameters:
      pCitationForm -
      Returns:
      String
